What you need to know:  In addition to the 1.75 million Euros (Sh219m) prize kitty this year, the sponsors have injected another Sh100m to Sh200m into the event in one form or another and this has been the case with Magical Kenya Open for many years now.Are we building a beautiful house on quick sand? Where are our golfing roots in Kenya? Where is the golf development agenda?Until these questions are answered, this picture will not change.